title: HATS-7b Exoplanet Transit Plot in Altair
creators:
    - Ellianna Schwab
    - Itamar Reis
description: >
Jupyter notebook of Jake VanderPlas's Altair tutorial (https://altair-viz.github.io/tutorials/getting-started.html) 
and Altair version of figure 1 from Bakos et al. 2015, 
which indicates the transit of HATS-7b in the lightcurve of HATS-7.
source-url: https://github.com/elliesch/PlotLibrary/blob/master/HATS-7b.ipynb
contact-github: elliesch
orcid: orcid.org/0000-0002-9879-1183
